Caption: At Open Air Theatre IIT Madras. On the stage Prof. B. Sengupto and Dr. H.C. Heinrich Luebke
Description: This event marked not only the visit of the President of the Federal Republic of Germany, but also the inauguration of the Open Air Theatre (OAT) of IIT Madras. The banner in the background reads "Herzlich Willkommen", which translates to "Warm Welcome".
